==Trivia==
*The names given in the crystal impling's examine texts refer to the individual names of implings found in {{RSL|Daffyd}}'s house in the Amlodd Clan district of ''RuneScape''<nowiki/>'s Prifddinas after having caught certain types of implings. These are named after the team of [[Jagex Moderator]]s who developed Prifddinas in ''RuneScape''.

